text: Nikoletta Nagy (born 26 October 1994) is a Hungarian model and beauty pageant titleholder who was crowned Miss Universe Hungary 2015 and represented Hungary in the Miss Universe 2015 and pageant. ==Personal life== Nagy is a student of Biological Engineering at Corvinus University of Budapest. ===Miss Universe Hungary 2015=== On 6 June 2015 Nagy was crowned Miss Universe Hungary 2015. The pageant was broadcast by TV2 Hungary. A total of sixteen contestants competed for the crown. ===Miss Universe 2015=== As Miss Hungary 2015, Nagy competed at the Miss Universe 2015 pageant in Las Vegas. == References == Category:Living people Category:Hungarian beauty pageant winners Category:1995 births Category:Miss Universe 2015 contestants
title: Nikoletta Nagy
